column5: Amazing! You're being so strong for not just avoiding self harm, but for sharing this as well. Here's hopefully to another 100! :)
My bf tells me that the therapists didn't help him with his issues, and he doesn't think they'll be as much help either. Feel like an ass
Used to be, but my sessions ended just before I moved in with my bf. I dont want to go back because they always tell me the same things. I'm probably just picky.
